     fhir:status [ fhir:v "extensions" ] ;
     fhir:div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet VSVFDiagnosticReportLabStatus-vista</b></p><a name=\"VSVFDiagnosticReportLabStatus-vista\"> </a><a name=\"hcVSVFDiagnosticReportLabStatus-vista\"> </a><a name=\"VSVFDiagnosticReportLabStatus-vista-en-US\"> </a><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v2-0123.html\"><code>http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v2-0123</code></a><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td><td><b><a href=\"ValueSet-VSVFDiagnosticReportLabStatus.html\">VF_DiagnosticReportLabStatus</a></b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v2-0123.html#v2-0123-C\">C</a></td><td>CORRECTED RESULTS</td><td>A result under an order, that has been finalized has been corrected</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-diagnostic-report-status.html#diagnostic-report-status-corrected\">corrected</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v2-0123.html#v2-0123-F\">F</a></td><td>FINAL RESULTS</td><td>Final results; results stored and verified.</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-diagnostic-report-status.html#diagnostic-report-status-final\">final</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v2-0123.html#v2-0123-Y\">Y</a></td><td>NO ORDER ON RECORD</td><td>No order on record for this test.</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-diagnostic-report-status.html#diagnostic-report-status-unknown\">unknown</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v2-0123.html#v2-0123-R\">R</a></td><td>NOT VERIFIED</td><td>Results stored; not yet verified</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-diagnostic-report-status.html#diagnostic-report-status-preliminary\">preliminary</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v2-0123.html#v2-0123-X\">X</a></td><td>ORDER CANCELED</td><td>No results available; Order canceled.</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-diagnostic-report-status.html#diagnostic-report-status-cancelled\">cancelled</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v2-0123.html#v2-0123-O\">O</a></td><td>ORDER RECIEVED</td><td>Order received; specimen not yet received</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-diagnostic-report-status.html#diagnostic-report-status-registered\">registered</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v2-0123.html#v2-0123-P\">P</a></td><td>PRELIMINARY</td><td>A verified early result is available, final results not yet obtained</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-diagnostic-report-status.html#diagnostic-report-status-preliminary\">preliminary</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v2-0123.html#v2-0123-S\">S</a></td><td>PROCEDURE SCHEDULED</td><td>No results available; procedure scheduled, but not done</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-diagnostic-report-status.html#diagnostic-report-status-registered\">registered</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v2-0123.html#v2-0123-A\">A</a></td><td>SOME RESULTS AVAILABLE</td><td>Some, but not all, results available</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-diagnostic-report-status.html#diagnostic-report-status-partial\">partial</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v2-0123.html#v2-0123-I\">I</a></td><td>SPECIMEN RECEIVED</td><t